        10
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://museumsdatabase.com/museums/view/22518"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "That station once served as a bustling transportation hub for the community until the mid‑20th century.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        10
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://museumsdatabase.com/museums/view/22518"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Its programs include lectures, walking tours, and exhibits that bring local history to life.",
